  <stage stageid="b1747b0d-0ceb-4fa3-b0cd-b9d77b0a0b3d" name="Create Bearer Token Cred" type="Action">
    <subsheetid>28bda44d-733c-4c9f-86d7-b168edd3406c</subsheetid>
    <narrative>
    </narrative>
    <displayx>150</displayx>
    <displayy>-30</displayy>
    <displaywidth>90</displaywidth>
    <displayheight>30</displayheight>
    <font family="Segoe UI" size="10" style="Regular" color="000000"/>
    <inputs>
      <input type="flag" name="Requires Login" narrative="Flag indicating if the login info should be given too" expr="True"/>
      <input type="text" name="Arguments" narrative="The arguments to pass to automatec, not including the authentication info" expr="&amp;quot;/createcredential &amp;quot;&amp;amp;[Bearer Token Credential Name]&amp;amp;&amp;quot; &amp;quot;&amp;quot;&amp;quot;&amp;quot; &amp;quot;&amp;quot;&amp;quot;&amp;quot; /credentialtype BearerToken&amp;quot;"/>
      <input type="text" name="Username" narrative="The username that you want to authenticate against." expr="&amp;quot;admin&amp;quot;"/>
      <input type="text" name="Password" narrative="The password for the username." expr="&amp;quot;admin&amp;quot;"/>
    </inputs>
    <outputs>
